messages.message:
Running through these steps, the following command failed for me
```> git remote | grep -v ib-upstream-tmp | xargs git remote rm
usage: git remote remove <name>```
Updating it to this (source (https://stackoverflow.com/a/28806991/3986235)) worked
```git remote | grep -v ib-upstream-tmp | tr '\n' '\0' | xargs -0 -n1 git remote rm```
Ah thanks! I wonder if the MacOS output is different from the GNU/Linux binaries. :pray::skin-tone-3: Thanks for sharing that!
